#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.159"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.159:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga "
msgstr "16. The True Teaching "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.159:0.3"
msgid "159. Udāyīsutta "
msgstr "159. With Udāyī "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.159:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an5.159:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery. "

msgctxt "an5.159:1.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā udāyī mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ desento nisinno hoti. "
msgstr "Now, at that time Venerable Udāyī was sitting teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of laypeople. "

msgctxt "an5.159:1.4"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivutaṃ dhammaṃ desentaṃ nisinnaṃ. "
msgstr "Seeing this, Venerable Ānanda "

msgctxt "an5.159:1.5"
msgid "Disvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: desento nisinnoti
msgctxt "an5.159:1.6"
msgid "“āyasmā, bhante, udāyī mahatiyā gihiparisāya parivuto dhammaṃ desetī”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, Venerable Udāyī is teaching Dhamma, surrounded by a large assembly of laypeople.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.159:2.1"
msgid "“Na kho, ānanda, sukaraṃ paresaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ. "
msgstr "“Ānanda, it’s not easy to teach Dhamma to others. "

msgctxt "an5.159:2.2"
msgid "Paresaṃ, ānanda, dhammaṃ desentena pañca dhamme ajjhattaṃ upaṭṭhāpetvā paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo. "
msgstr "You should establish five things in yourself before teaching Dhamma to others. "

msgctxt "an5.159:2.3"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: Anupubbiṃ kathaṃ → ānupubbikathaṃ (bj) | anupubbikathaṃ (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.159:2.4"
msgid "‘Anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo; "
msgstr "You should teach Dhamma to others thinking: ‘I will teach step by step.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.5"
msgid "‘pariyāyadassāvī kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo; "
msgstr "‘I will teach explaining my methods.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.6"
msgid "‘anuddayataṃ paṭicca kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo; "
msgstr "‘I will teach out of kindness.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.7"
msgid "‘na āmisantaro kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo; "
msgstr "‘I will not teach while secretly hoping to profit.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.8"
msgid "‘attānañca parañca anupahacca kathaṃ kathessāmī’ti paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo. "
msgstr "‘I will teach without hurting myself or others.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.159:2.9"
msgid "Na kho, ānanda, sukaraṃ paresaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ. "
msgstr "It’s not easy to teach Dhamma to others. "

msgctxt "an5.159:2.10"
msgid "Paresaṃ, ānanda, dhammaṃ desentena ime pañca dhamme ajjhattaṃ upaṭṭhāpetvā paresaṃ dhammo desetabbo”ti. "
msgstr "You should establish these five things in yourself before teaching Dhamma to others.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.159:2.11"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

